channel.title: I can't think of any more commands
channel.description: Okay, so I've created about 5 or 6 commands.... Well, I'm still trying to think of some commands for my server. So my next command will be... Shit, I'm stumped! Please help me! :( I can't think of any so I am currently accepting commands for the given time. I will accept many commands, as long as if they are UNIQUE! I want something that's NOT average, like starter and party hat commands, for instance, I want something DIFFERENT! So post it below! You know, downwards... I really need a command that would put a little bit of SPARK in it. Here's my statement: <><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><> ============================================================================================= <><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><><> [b]1.[/b] It has to be UNIQUE! [b]2.[/b] I will put YOUR name into the message if I use it. [b]3.[/b] If it's completely perfect, like one like "I should've thought of that BEFORE!" I may make you admin or mod. [b]4.[/b] Don't send me a stupid starter command. I already have one. [b]5.[/b] Don't tell me how to make commands because I do. The only reason I'm doing this is because I've run out of ideas. [b]6.[/b] Don't make it something stupid. [b]7.[/b] I won't accept many so GET ON IT!
